data.name: Literal.Error.Address.Apartment
data.value: Kua ngaro, kāore rānei i kitea te tau whare noho. Whakatika i tō wāhitau.
data.comment: The error message for invalid apartment number.

data.name: Literal.Error.Address.Charset
data.value: Me whakamahi anake i ngā pūāhua Ingarihi.
data.comment: The error message when data is in charset that is not supported by address verification.

data.name: Literal.Error.Address.DoubleConfirm
data.value: Kāore e taea tō wāhitau te manatoko. Manatokona tō wāhitau ka pāwhiri "Panuku >".
data.comment: The error message when address verification system requires user to double confirm the address.

data.name: Literal.Error.Address.ID
data.value: He muhu te tau whare noho. Whakatika i tō wāhitau.
data.comment: The error message for invalid apartment ID.

data.name: Literal.Error.Address.Insufficient
data.value: He muhu te wāhitau Whakatika i tō wāhitau.
data.comment: The error message for insufficient information for address.

data.name: Literal.Error.Address.InvalidData
data.value: He muhu te wāhitau, whakatikahia tō wāhitau.
data.comment: The error message when data is missing for address verification.

data.name: Literal.Error.Address.Multiple
data.value: He muhu te wāhitau, whakatikahia tō wāhitau.
data.comment: The error message for invalid address.

data.name: Literal.Error.Address.Pobox
data.value: Kāore te Pouaka Poutāpeta i te tautokona. Tēnā, homai tō wāhitau.
data.comment: The error message for POBOX.

data.name: Literal.Error.Address.PostalCode
data.value: Kāore te waehere pōhi i kitea. Whakatika i tō wāhitau.
data.comment: The error message for invalid postal code.

data.name: Literal.Error.Address.Route
data.value: Kāore te pūtāutu ratonga huarahi i kitea, kei waho rānei i te awhe. Whakatika i tō wāhitau.
data.comment: The error message for route service error.

data.name: Literal.Error.Address.Street
data.value: Kāore te ingoa tiriti i kitea i te waehere pōhi i tohua. Whakatika i tō wāhitau.
data.comment: The error message for route service error.

data.name: Literal.Error.AuthzFail
data.value: Kāore e taea te whakamana te tikanga utu. Me tirotiro e tika ana ngā mōhiohio, whakamahia tētahi atu tikanga utu rānei. Ki te whiwhi tonu koe i tēnei karere, me whakapā atu ki tō whakahaere pūtea.
data.comment: The error message shown when card authorization fails.

data.name: Literal.Error.AuthzFail2
data.value: I puta mai he raru i te whakamanatanga o tō taputapu utu. Tēnā whakapā mai ki ratonga kiritaki mā rātou e āwhina.
data.comment: The error message shown when card authorization fails. Probably, the PI is rejected by risk.

data.name: Literal.Error.AuthzFail.BR
data.value: Kāore i taea tēnei tauwhitinga te whakamana. Me manatoko ō mōhiohio. Kāore pea e whakaaetia kei tēnei pūhara ētahi kāri utunga, nā reira i tēnei wā, e tūtohu ana mātou kia whakamahia he kāri utunga kē. Ki te raru tonu, me whakapā koe ki tō umanga pūtea.
data.comment: The error message shown when card authorization fails in Brazil. Probably, the debit / credit card that the user tried to add is not accepted.

data.name: Literal.Error.AuthzFail.MX
data.value: Kāore i taea tēnei tauwhitinga te whakamana. Me manatoko ō mōhiohio. Kāore pea e whakaaetia e te pūhara utunga ētahi kāri utunga nā ngā kaupapahere haumarutanga kua whakatakotoria. Ki te raru tonu, me whakapā koe ki tō umanga pūtea.
data.comment: The error message shown when card authorization fails in Mexico. Probably, the debit / credit card that the user tried to add is not accepted.

data.name: Literal.Error.CardUsedMuiltipleTimes
data.value: Kua tāpiri atu tō tikanga utu ki ngā pūkete maha rawa. Me ngana anō me tētahi atu.
data.comment: The error message shown when user tries to add an card is used too many times.

data.name: Literal.Error.CcExpired
data.value: Kua pau tō kāri nama. Tēnā, tīpakona tētahi rā pau hei ngā rā e tū mai nai.
data.comment: The error message shown when the credit card is expired.

data.name: Literal.Error.CcNumberInvalid
data.value: He muhu tō tau kāri tāwere. Tēnā, tāurua he tau kāri tāwere whaimana.
data.comment: The error message shown when the credit card number is invalid.

data.name: Literal.Error.DdBankCodeInvalid
data.value: He muhu tō tau ararere, tēnā, tāurua ngā mōhiohio whaimana.
data.comment: The error message shown when the direct debit bank code is invalid.

data.name: Literal.Error.DdBranchCodeInvalid
data.value: He muhu tō waehere kōmaka, tēnā, tāurua ngā mōhiohio whaimana.
data.comment: The error message shown when the direct debit branch code is invalid.

data.name: Literal.Error.DdNumberInvalid
data.value: He muhu tō tau pūkete, tēnā, tāurua ngā mōhiohio whaimana.
data.comment: The error message shown when the direct debit account number is invalid.

data.name: Literal.Error.AccountIdInvalid
data.comment: The error message is shown when the billable account id is invalid.

data.name: Literal.Error.AccountLocked
data.comment: The error message is shown when the billable account is locked or disabled.

data.name: Literal.Error.EnterValidInfo
data.comment: The error message shown when user enters invalid information.

data.name: Literal.Error.EnterValidInfo2
data.value: He muhu ō mōhiohio tikanga utu. Ki te puta tonu mai tēnei karere, kia ngana anō ki tētahi atu tikanga utu, whakapā mai rānei ki ratonga kiritaki mā rātou e āwhina.
data.comment: The error message shown when user enters invalid information.

data.name: Literal.Error.InvalidAddress
data.value: He muhu tō wāhitau, tēnā, tāurua ngā mōhiohio whaimana.
data.comment: The error message shown when the address is invalid.

data.name: Literal.Error.InvalidAddress2
data.value: He muhu tō wāhitau. Āta titiro he tika katoa ō mōhiohio wāhitau.
data.comment: The error message shown when the address is invalid.

data.name: Literal.Error.InvalidCity
data.value: He muhu tō tāone nui, tāurua ngā mōhiohio whaimana.
data.comment: The error message shown when the city is invalid.

data.name: Literal.Error.InvalidPhoneType
data.value: He muhu ō raraunga waea, me tāuru he mōhiohio whaimana.
data.comment: The error message shown when the phone type is not valid.

data.name: Literal.Error.InvalidState
data.value: He muhu tō whenua tōpū, tēnā, tāurua ngā mōhiohio whaimana.
data.comment: The error message shown when the state is invalid.

data.name: Literal.Error.InvalidZipcode
data.value: He muhu tō waehere ZIP, tēnā, tāurua ngā mōhiohio whaimana.
data.comment: The error message shown when the zipcode is invalid.

data.name: Literal.Error.PhoneNumberRequired
data.value: Kei te hiahiatia te tau waea.
data.comment: The error message shown when the phone number is missing.

data.name: Literal.Error.PiAlreadyExists
data.value: Kāore i taea tēnei tikanga utu, nā te mea kei roto kē tēnei i tō pūkete. Me ngana anō me tētahi atu.
data.comment: The error message shown when user tries to add an card that is already added.

data.name: Literal.Error.PiAlreadyExists2
data.value: Kāore e taea e mātou te tikanga utu te tāpiri. Āta titiro kāore anō kia tāpiritia ki tō pūkete. Ki te puta tonu mai tēnei karere, kia ngana anō ki tētahi atu tikanga utu, whakapā mai rānei ki ratonga kiritaki mā rātou e āwhina.
data.comment: The error message shown when user tries to add an card that is already added.

data.name: Literal.Error.PiBanned
data.value: Kua rāhui tō tikanga utu. Me ngana anō me tētahi atu.
data.comment: The error message shown when the PI is banned.

data.name: Literal.Error.PiExceedMaxOwnership
data.value: Kua whakamahia te mōhiohio nāu i hōmai e ngā pūkete maha rawa atu. Tāuru i tētahi pūkete anō, tētahi wāhitau rānei.
data.comment: The error message shown when user tries to add a pi which has been used by other accounts for many times.

data.name: Literal.Error.PiLimitExceeded
data.value: Kāore e taea te manakotanga utu te tāpiri. Whakamahia tētahi manakohanga utu tīari, tangohia rānei tētahi manakohanga utu.
data.comment: The error message shown when paper check last name is not correct.

data.name: Literal.Error.SaInIntermediateStatus
data.value: Kāore e taea tō tono te tutuki i tēnei wā, nā te mea ka namahia tō kāri nama i tēnei rā mō tētahi o ō ohaurunga. Whakamātauhia tētahi atu kāri, ngana anō ā kō ake rānei.
data.comment: The error message shown when the PI is in intermediate status.

data.name: Literal.Consent.Content.AR
data.value:
Kia horaina mai he hua, he ratonga rānei ki a koe, he mea nui kia hanga koe i tētahi pūkete kaiwhakamahi. I ngā wā katoa e hora mai ai koe i tētahi tikanga utu hōu mō tētahi hua, tētahi ratonga rānei, mā mātou pea e tuku atu te pānui e whai ake nei me te rapu i tō whakaaetanga i mua i tō haerenga whakamua. I roto i ngā mahi hanga pūkete, te tāpiri tikanga utu hou hoki/rānei, hei āwhina hoki i aua mahi, me mātua hora mai e koe ngā raraunga whaiaro pēnei i: tō ingoa, tō wāhi noho, tō tau waea, tō wāhitau īmēra, tō tau kāri tāwere me tō tau pūkete pēke. Ka kohia hoki pea e mātou tō wāhitau IP me tō TT pūrere, ka whakapiri ai i tēnei mōhiohio ki ngā raraunga whaiaro kua horaina mai e koe mō te hanga pūkete, mō te tāpiri rānei i tētahi tikanga utu hou.
Kei te tino whakaae au kia whakamahi Microsoft Corporation, ōna hoa kamupene me ōna pekanga, kia whakamahi i ngā raraunga whaiaro kua horaina atu e ahau i roto nei, i runga anō i ngā whakaritenga e tākina atu nei e te Ture Tau. 25,326, Tekihana 5 mō ngā āhuatanga pēnei i te tuku pānuitanga mai ki ahau, ngā rauemi whakatairanga rānei mō ā rātou tāpaetanga, ratonga rānei. E kī tūturu ana au i konei, i raro anō i te Ture Tau 25,326, Tekihana 6, kua whakamōhiotia mai au kei au te tikanga mō te whakaaetanga nei.
Ki te kore e horaina mai ngā raraunga, e kore tētehi āhuatanga e pā mai i muri, hāunga te korenga e taea ngā hua me ngā ratonga te whakauru atu mā roto i tēnei whārangi tukutuku. Ki te hora au i tēnei raraunga, kua tino tāpae i taku whakaaetanga ki te whakaputu atu i aua raraunga i te patengi raraunga o te Microsoft Corporation e noho rā i Redmond, WA 98052. Ka taea e te kaipupuri o ngā raraunga whaiaro te kawe i āna tika kia uru atu ki aua raraunga, i ētahi wā rānei kia kaua e iti iho i te ono marama, hāunga ngā urunga e puta mai ai he taunakitanga he pānga tōtika tō te tangata, pērā i tā Ture Tau. 25,326, Tekihana 14, Tekihana o raro 3. Ko te mana whakahaere i te whakaūnga o Ture 25,326 ko te ARGENTINE DIRECTORATE OF PERSONAL DATA PROTECTION kua oti hoki tērā rōpū te whakamana hei wherawhera i tētahi amuamu/kerēme hoki/rānei ka kawea i runga i te pūtake o te kore e ū ki ngā whakaritenga mō te kaupare raraunga whaiaro.
Ka taea e koe te uru te whakarerekē rānei i ō raraunga whaiaro i: https://commerce.microsoft.com. Ki te kōwhiri koe kia whakarerekē i ō raraunga whaiaro mā reira kua whakaae koe ki te kohikohi me te rokiroki a Microsoft Corporation i ō raraunga whaiaro, pēra i runga nei.
Mā te hanga pūkete me te pāwhiri i te pātene "Whakaae" i raro iho nei kei te whakaae koe kia kohikohi kia rokiroki hoki Microsoft Corporation i ō raraunga whaiaro, me te whakaae kia kohikohi kia whakawhiti Microsoft Corporation e pēra i ngā kōrero e tākina atu nei.

data.name: Literal.Consent.Content.HU
data.value:
Kia horaina mai he hua, he ratonga rānei ki a koe, he mea nui kia hanga koe i tētahi pūkete kaiwhakamahi. I ngā wā katoa e hora mai ai koe i tētahi tikanga utu hōu mō tētahi hua, tētahi ratonga rānei, mā mātou pea e tuku atu te pānui e whai ake nei me te rapu i tō whakaaetanga i mua i tō haerenga whakamua. I roto i ngā mahi hanga pūkete, te tāpiri tikanga utu hou hoki/rānei, hei āwhina hoki i aua mahi, me mātua hora mai e koe ētahi raraunga whaiaro ka taea te tautohu pēnei i: tō ingoa, tō wāhi noho, tō tau waea, tō wāhitau īmēra, tō tau kāri tāwere me tō tau pūkete pēke. Ka kohia hoki pea e mātou tō wāhitau IP me tō TT pūrere, ka whakapiri ai i tēnei mōhiohio ki ngā raraunga whaiaro ka taea te tautohu kua horaina mai e koe mō te hanga pūkete, mō te tāpiri rānei i tētahi tikanga utu hou.
Ka kohia, ka whakawhitia inamata ēnei mōhiohio whaiaro ka taea te tautohu i te hanganga pūkete i runga i ngā tikanga muna, haumaru hoki ki Microsoft Corporation i Amerika, hei tukatuka i ō whakawhitinga hei hora hoki i ngā hua me ngā ratonga ki a koe. Ka whakamahia pea ka puritia hoki mō te roanga o te wā e whakaaetia ana e te ture. E kore a Microsoft Corporation e whakamahi ō mōhiohio whaiaro ka taea te tautohu mō ngā pūtake i tua atu i ērā e tākina atu nei i konei, tae atu, engari kāore e herea anake, ki ngā mahi hokohoko.
E kore a Microsoft e whākī i ō mōhiohio whaiaro ka taea te tautohu ki te hunga tuatoru. Ka whakawhitiria ō mōhiohio ki te hunga tuatoru mehemea me pērā anake e taea ai tō whakawhitinga te tukatuka, te whakahāngai rānei i ngā mahi ki ngā ritenga ā-ture, te urupare rānei ki ngā kerēme, te aukati i te mahi tinihanga, i raro rānei i ngā ritenga o te kāwanatanga.
Ka taea e koe te uru te whakarerekē rānei i ō mōhiohio whaiaro ka taea te tautohu i: https://commerce.microsoft.com. Ki te kōwhiri koe kia whakarerekē i ō mōhiohio mā reira kua whakaae koe ki te kohikohi me te whakawhiti inamata a Microsoft Corporation i ō mōhiohio whaiaro ka taea te tautohu, pēra i runga nei.
Mā te hanga pūkete me te pāwhiri i te pātene "Whakaae" i raro iho nei kei te whakaae koe kia kohikohi kia rokiroki hoki Microsoft Corporation i ō mōhiohio whaiaro ka taea te tautohu, me te whakaae kia kohikohi kia whakawhiti kia tiri hoki a Microsoft Corporation i ō mōhiohio whaiaro ka taea te tautohu ki te hunga tuatoru pēra i ngā kōrero e tākina atu nei.

data.name: Literal.PICVC.TermOfUse.Content
data.value:
• Ka namatia tō kāri tāwere i waenga i {0} {1} - {2} mō tētahi rahinga tē whakaaturia.
  • Ka whakahokia te rahinga i namatia ki a koe ina oti te tukanga manatoko.
  • E manatokona ai koe, me tāuru koe te tino rahinga pū i namatia, TĒNEI RĀNEI me whakauru te waehere 3 mati e hora mai ana i te whakaahua whakawhitinga.
  • Ka kitea pea e koe te rahinga i namatia, te waehere 3-mati rānei mā te tiro ki tō tauākī kāri tāwere. Kei te āhua tonu o ngā ratonga o tō pēke, ka taea tēnei te mahi tuihono, ā-waea, ā-tauākī pepa ka tae mai i te mēra rānei.
  • Me mātua whakaoti te manatokonga i mua i te {3}, ā, e {4} ō āheinga kia whakamātau anō.
  • Kei te āhua o tō tauwāhi me te tauwāhi o te pēke nāna tō kāri i whakaputa, ka nama pea te pēke i tētahi Utunga Whakawhitinga ā-Ao (ITF), ka hoatu rānei i ngā namanga whakawhitinga moni i te tapeke i namatia i roto i te tukanga manatoko. Hei whakatau mēnā ka pā pea aua utunga, āta kōrero ki te pēke nāna tō kāri i whakaputa. E KORE ngā utunga ITF, whakawhitinga moni rānei ka ara ake i te hātepe manatoko e whakahokia e Microsoft.

data.name: Literal.PICVCDDPayin.TermOfUse.Content
data.value:
• Ka namatia tō pūtea pēke i waenga i {0} {1} - {2} mō tētahi rahinga tē whakaaturia.
  • Ka whakahokia te rahinga i namatia ki a koe ina oti te tukanga manatoko.
  • E manatokona ai koe, me tāuru koe te tino rahinga pū i namanatia, TĒNEI RĀNEI me whakauru te waehere 3 mati e hora mai ana i te whakaahua whakawhitinga.
  • Ka kitea pea e koe te rahinga i namatia, te waehere 3-mati rānei mā te tiro ki tō tauākī pūtea pēke. Kei te āhua tonu o ngā ratonga o tō pēke, ka taea tēnei te mahi tuihono, ā-waea, ā-tauākī pepa ka tae mai i te mēra rānei.
  • Me mātua whakaoti te manatokonga i mua i te {3}, ā, e {4} ō āheinga kia whakamātau anō.
  • Kei te āhua o tō tauwāhi me te tauwāhi o te pēke nāna tō pūtea i whakaputa, ka nama pea te pēke i tētahi Utunga Whakawhitinga ā-Ao (ITF), ka hoatu rānei i ngā namanga whakawhitinga moni i te tapeke i namatia i roto i te tukanga manatoko. Hei whakatau mēnā ka pā pea aua utunga, āta kōrero ki te pēke nāna tō pūtea i whakaputa. E KORE ngā utunga ITF, whakawhitinga moni rānei ka ara ake i te hātepe manatoko e whakahokia e Microsoft.
data.comment: PICVC DDPayin term of use. {0} is for the currency. {1} is for the min amount to charge. {2} is for the max amount to charge. {3} is the exact time of challenge deadline. {4} is the left times to retry challenge.

data.name: Literal.CreditCheck.SSNInfo
data.value: Ka kohikohia tō Tau Haumarutanga Pāpori (SSN) i a koe, ka tiria ki tētahi hunga-tuatoru ngaio hei whakahaere i tētahi takitaki pūtea hei whakatau mēnā he pai kia whiwhi koe i te tāpaetanga. Ka whakamahia ngā tikanga hangarau hei āwhina ki te pare atu i te urunga manakore ki te whakamahi, ki te puakanga rānei o ngā SSN. Ka whakawhitia te SSN i runga i te whatunga haumaru, ka whakamunatia i mua i te whakawhitinga. E kore mātou e pupuri i te SSN i muri i te whakatutukitanga o te takitaki pūtea, ahakoa ka pupuritia tētahi pūtāutu ahurei mai i tō SSN mō te mana auau te take. Ka puritia hoki e mātou te tapeke pūtea me ētahi atu mōhiohio ka tīkina hei wāhanga o te takitaki pūtea mō te wā e tika ana ki te tutuki i tō tauwhitinga, mō te hopuranga me te āraitanga i te mahi tinihanga te take.
data.comment: Info for SSN.

data.name: Literal.CreditCheck.ThingsToKnow
data.value:
E kore pea tēnei tākinga pūtea e pā ki tō tauranga pūtea.
Ka whakamahia tō tau social security kia pai ai tā mātou kawe i tētahi tākinga pūtea, me te whakatau kua āhei koe kia whiwhi i te tāpaetanga.
Ka taea e koe te mahi huringa ki ō mōhiohio utunga, nama hoki ā tōna wā mā te haere ki https://live.xbox.com/en-US/account
data.comment: Things to know on credit check.

data.name: Word.SEPA.TermConditions
data.value: Mā te whamamahi i tēnei whakamananga, kua kōwhiri koe i ngā Utu Taunoa hei whakaritenga utu māu. Ka herea tō whakamahi i Utu Taunoa ki tō whakaae me tō ū ki ēnei whakaritenga. Kei te whakamana koe i Microsoft Payments Ltd. ("mātou" "mātourānei") kia tono utu ki tō pēke mō ngā moni e tika ana kia utua ki Microsoft. Me mātua whakarite koe: (i) kua tukua mai e koe he wāhitau ī-mēra tōtika mō ngā reta me ngā whakawhitinga kōrero; (ii) ka whakaae tō pēke ki ngā kohinga utu taunoa; (iii)he moni rawaka āu i te rā i whakaritea hei utunga; ā, (iv) kāore anō tō whakamananga kia whakakorea (hāunga ngā āhuatanga i raro iho nei) kāore anō hoki kia whakakorea. Ki te kore te tangata e ū ki ēnei whakaritenga me te kore pea e utua te nama, kāore e ngaro te here i a koe kia utu i a mātou i ngā nama e taurewa ana, e tika ana kia utua. Tēnā whakapā mai ki a mātou ki te whakakore i tēnei whakamananga, ki te tīpako rānei i tētahi atu momo utunga. Mā mātou e whakakore tō whakamananga i te taenga mai o tō whakamōhiotanga. Kei a mātou te tikanga o te whakaae ki te Utu Taunoa, kāore rānei, ā, ki te kore e wātea i roto i te wā, mā mātou e whakapā atu ki a koe ki te whakarite tikanga kē.
data.comment: The content of "Term & Conditions" for SEPA.

Ki te kore te tangata e ū ki ēnei whakaritenga me te kore pea e utua te nama, kāore e ngaro te here i a koe kia utu i a mātou i ngā nama e taurewa ana, e tika ana kia utua. Tēnā whakapā mai ki a mātou ki te whakakore i tēnei whakamananga, ki te tīpako rānei i tētahi atu momo utunga. Mā mātou e whakakore tō whakamananga i te taenga mai o tō whakamōhiotanga. Kei a mātou te tikanga o te whakaae ki te Utu Taunoa, kāore rānei, ā, ki te kore e wātea i roto i te wā, mā mātou e whakapā atu ki a koe ki te whakarite tikanga kē.

data.name: Literal.ACH.SubscriptionAgreement
data.value: Mā te taki i tēnei pouaka, kei te whakamana koe i (A) Microsoft Payments Ltd. ("Microsoft") kia tuku i ngā tohutohu ki tō pēke kia namatia tō pūkete, ā, i (B) tō pēke hoki kia namatia tō pūkete i runga anō i ngā tohutohu mai i Microsoft. Hei wāhi anō o ō tika, kua whai mana koe kia whiwhi whakahokinga moni mai i tō pēke i raro i ngā whakaritenga me ngā here o tō whakaaetanga ki tō pēke. Me mātua kerēme te whakahokinga moni i roto i te 8 wiki mai i te rā i namatia ai tō pūkete. E whakamāramatia ana ō tika i roto i tētahi tauākī ka riro mai i tō pēke.

data.name: Literal.ACH.SubscriptionAgreement.New
data.value: Mā te rēhita, te tīpako rānei i tō pūtea pēke hei tikanga utu māu, kei te whakaae koe kia tīmata a Microsoft (tētahi o ana ringaringa rānei) i tētahi namanga, i ētahi namanga rānei mō te tapeke katoa (tae atu ki ngā tāke whai pānga, ngā utu me ngā utu tukunga) o tō hoko, tō nama ohauru rānei (i runga anō i ngā whakaritenga o tō ratonga ohauru) mai i tō pūtea pēke, (ā, mehemea e tika ana, kia tīmata ētahi tāwere ki tō pūtea pēke hei whakatika hapa, hei whakahoki moni, me ērā momo kaupapa), ā, kei te whakaae koe kia tangohia e tō whakahaere moni, kei reira tō pūtea pēke e puritia ana, ētahi namanga pērā, kia whakawhiwhia rānei ki rānei aua tāwere. Kei te mārama koe ka noho mana tonu tēnei whakamananga taea noatia tō tango i tō mōhiohio pūtea pēke i tō pūkete Microsoft, i tō pūkete Skype rānei.

data.name: Literal.ACH.SubscriptionAgreement.MSfB

data.name: Literal.Error.PolicyReject

data.name: Literal.Inicis.BrowserMsg
data.value: Kāore e āhei ngā kiritaki e whakamahi ana i ngā pūtirotiro tukutuku ehara i te IE (Internet Explorer) ki te waitohu mō ngā ratonga Azure hōu, nā tētahi raru tāutanga ActiveX. Whakamahia te IE, tētahi VM (Virtual Machine) rānei me te IE hei waitohu. Ka oti te tikanga utunga te rēhita, ka āhei koe ki te whakamahi i ērā atu pūtirotiro tukutuku mō ngā ratonga Azure. E whakapāha ana mātou mō tēnei raruraru.
data.comment: Only need localization for Korean, other markets do not use it

data.name: Literal.Inicis.BrowserMsgActiveX
data.value: Nā te mea i ahu mai tēnei tomokanga utu i ActiveX, mēnā kei te whakamahi koe i tētahi atu pūtirotiro (tae atu ki Microsoft Edge), hāunga a Internet Explorer, kāore e taea te whakahohe i Azure. Whakamahia a Internet Explorer ki te waitohu. Mutu mai te waitohu, ka taea te whakamahi tētahi pūtirotiro ahakoa tēhea. Aroha noa mō tēnei raruraru.
data.comment: Only need localization for Korean, other markets do not use it

data.name: Literal.Inicis.NameMsg

data.name: Literal.CIBUpgradeTOU.SubHeader
data.value: Ka taea e koe ināianei te whakamahi ngā whakamananga utunga tōmua Microsoft ahakoa te wāhi mēnā kei te wātea a PayPal, ina utu koe mā Microsoft.

data.name: Literal.CIBUpgradeTOU.MigrationText.US
data.value: Whakamahi i Paypal mō ngā utunga kei mua i te pūhara Microsoft. Mēnā he toenga PayPal tāu, koirā ka whakamahia tuatahitia, ahakoa kua kōwhiria e koe he tikanga utu manako. Mēnā kāore anō koe kia kōwhiri i tētahi tikanga utu manako, ka whakamahia tuatahitia tō tikanga utu taunoa. Mēnā kua pau kua whakakāhoretia rānei tō tikanga utu manako, taunoa rānei, ka namatia e PayPal tō tikanga utu tārua. Ka taea e koe te tautuhi te huri rānei tō tikanga utu, te whakakāhore rānei i tō whakamananga ahakoa te wā i Ngā Tautuhinga at PayPal.com. Kia oti rā anō tō tikanga utu te tatū i ō Tautuhinga, ka whai te tikanga utu i ngā kaupapahere utunga i PayPal.com.
data.comment: Text for United States, Canada, Brazil

data.name: Literal.CIBUpgradeTOU.MigrationText.DE
data.value: Kei te whakaae koe ka āhei a Microsoft te whakawhiti ō tohutohu utunga ki PayPal, kia pai ai tō utu hāngai i PayPal mō Microsoft ki Microsoft me ngā tāngata whiwhi utunga i tautuhitia e whakamahi ana i te pūhara Microsoft. Kei te whakaae koe kia tiri a PayPal i ō taipitopito tauwhitinga PayPal ki Microsoft tae atu ki ngā mōhiotanga ka tiria i te nuinga o te wā ki tētahi tangata whiwhi utunga i raro i tā mātou Kaupapahere Tūmataitinga. Mā konei ka āhei Microsoft ki te tiro mehemea kua tutuki tō utunga, e āwhina hoki te whakatutuki i te tauwhitinga. Mā PayPal a Microsoft e whakamōhio ki te kōunu koe i tō whakaae. Kei te tohutohu koe i PayPal kia whakaritea ngā tono utunga ka tukua e Microsoft hei utunga kua whakaaetia e koe. Mēnā he toenga PayPal tāu, koirā ka whakamahia tuatahitia. Ki te whakakāhoretia tō puna pūtea taunoa, kua pau rānei, ka namatia tō puna pūtea tārua. Ka taea e koe tēnei whakamananga te whakakore, te huri rānei i tō puna pūtea manako ahakoa te wā i roto i pūkete PayPal. Ki te utu koe mā tētahi moni ehara i te moni tuatahi o tō pūkete PayPal o nāianei, ka whakatahuritia te rahi e PayPal mā te whakamahi i tā mātou ritenga o taua wā.
data.comment: Text for Germany, Netherlands, Sweden, United Kingdom, Russia

data.name: Literal.MSFB.OrgProfile.LegalText
data.value: I ngā wā e pā āna, me homai ngā kiritaki EU i ngā taipitopito o tō rātou tau rēhita VAT. Ki te kore e pēnei ka pā pea tēnei ki te tukatanga VAT o te nama ka whakaputaina e Microsoft.

data.name: Literal.EG.OrgProfile.LegalText
data.value: I ngā wā e pā āna, me homai ngā kiritaki nō Ihipa i ngā taipitopito o ō rātou tau rēhita VAT tika. Mei kore e pēnei ka pā pea tēnei ki te tukatanga VAT o te nama nā Microsoft i whakaputa ai.
data.comment: Egypt update organization profile legal text

data.name: Literal.MSFB.OrgProfile.LegalText.NZ.Line1
data.value: Ka pā te tāke tāpiri o Aotearoa (NZ GST) at 15% ki ngā ratonga me ngā mahi kiko-kore whakawhiti-taupā a te hunga kāore e noho i reira, mā tētahi tangata kei Aotearoa e noho ana, hāunga ngā wā he kamupene rēhita mō GST taua hunga. Me mea te kaituku ko taua tangata whiwhi ehara i te tangata rēhita, ki te kore te tangata whiwhi e whakamōhio te kaituku he tangata rēhita ia, me te hoatu hoki i tana tau rēhita GST o Aotearoa.
data.comment: MSFB update organization profile legal text for New Zealand

data.name: Literal.MSFB.OrgProfile.LegalText.NZ.Line2
data.value: Hei āwhina i tēnei hononga, tēnā homai te tau rēhita GST o Aotearoa o tō umanga. Ki te kore ka namatia pea koe mō te GST o Aotearoa i te 15%, mō ā mātou tukunga ki a koe.
data.comment: MSFB update organization profile legal text for New Zealand

data.name: Literal.MSFB.OrgProfile.LegalText.NZ.Line3
data.value: Ki te rerekē te tau rēhita GST o Aotearoa o tō umanga, ki te whakarere rānei tō umanga i tōna rēhitatanga ā tōna wā mō GST i Aotearoa, tēnā whakamōhiotia mai mātou inamata.
data.comment: MSFB update organization profile legal text for New Zealand

data.name: Literal.MSFB.OrgProfile.LegalText.BR.Line1
data.value: Tēnā tāurutia he CNPJ mehemea he hinonga/tuakiri ā-ture koe. Ki te kore koe e tāuru i tētahi CNPJ ka kīa koe he tangata takitahi.

data.name: Literal.MSFB.OrgProfile.LegalText.UnknownCountries
data.value: Mō tēnei tono, me nama ngā whakaaetanga tāwere tāpiri mā tētahi pire. Tēnā tīpakona tēnei pouaka taki hei whakaae ki tētahi tirohanga tāwere. Ka whakapāngia atu koe mō ētahi atu kōrero. Ka noho tārewa te whakaae ki te tono, ā, kāore hoki e taea te toha raihana tāpiri, kia whakaaetia rā anō te tāwere. Ka haere pea tēnei tukanga mō te rua wiki pea. data.name: Literal.PayPalUpdateAgreement.Subheading

data.name: Literal.PayPalUpdateAgreement.Text
data.value: You agree to allow Microsoft to transmit your PayPal payment instructions to PayPal for purchases directly to Microsoft or an identified payment recipient utilizing a Microsoft platform. If you have a PayPal balance, it will be used first. If your preferred or default funding source is declined or expired, your backup-funding source will be charged. You allow PayPal to share your PayPal transaction details with Microsoft. The sharing of PayPal transaction details enables Microsoft to know if your payment has been successful, to help fulfill your transaction and provide payment receipts as identified in PayPal's Privacy Policy. You instruct PayPal to treat payment requests sent by Microsoft as authorized by you per the PayPal User Agreement. If you pay in a currency that is not the primary currency of your PayPal Account, PayPal will convert the amount using our then current rate. You can cancel this authorization or change your preferred funding source at any time in your PayPal account. If you withdraw your consent to use PayPal on Microsoft, PayPal may inform Microsoft.
data.comment: PayPal Scenario Strings - Agreement text for the update Paypal billing agreement page

data.name: Literal.CreditCard.CVVHelpDialogTextCloseCVVButton
data.value: Ko te CVV te Tau Manatoko Kāri i tō kāri tāwere, kāri nama rānei. I ngā kāri Visa, MasterCard me Discover, ko te CVV ngā tau whakamutunga e 3 kei muri o tō kāri. I ngā kāri American Express, ko te CVV te tau 4 mati kei mua o te kāri, i runga ake i te tau kāri matua. Kati te kōrerorero CVV.
data.comment: This is the text for the CVV help dialog

data.name: Literal.CreditCard.WhereIsMyCvvLast3DigitsText
data.value: Kei hea toku CVV? Ko ngā mati whakamutunga e 3 kei muri.
data.comment: This is the hint for CVV textbox in xboxnative

data.name: Literal.CreditCard.WhereIsMyCvvFront4DigitsText
data.value: Kei hea toku CVV? Ko te waehere 4-mati kei mua.
data.comment: This is the hint for CVV amex textbox in xboxnative
